nodes.text: TK-510 was a stormtrooper commander of the Galactic Empire.
In 1 ABY TK-510 was part of a stormtrooper unit that guarded a statue of Emperor Palpatine, which was installed in front of the Theed Royal Palace on Naboo during that year's Empire Day celebrations.
TK-510 was a Non-Player Character (NPC) in the MMORPG Star Wars Galaxies. He made appearances during the Empire Day live events of 2008 and 2009.
